      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i need to talk to someone about something weird that happened. i was looking at this cracked coffee mug on my counter this morning and i saw this flash in the reflection—it was like a glimpse of a car crash on the highway. then like twenty minutes later, the news reported a pileup on the I-95. it's starting to happen a lot lately. i feel like i'm seeing things before they actually happen. like i can see the echoes of what's coming?",
